          <a href="#chapter1.6a" data-target-id="chapter1.6a" class="p05__link  twtr-type--bold-16  twtr-color--purple-dark  has-hover">Twitterと共有する情報の管理方法</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="p05__wrapper  p05__wrapper-mobile">
      <div class="p05__title-wrapper">
        <div class="p05__title-content">
          <span class="p05__title  twtr-type--bold-16  twtr-color--purple-dark">&nbsp;</span>
